data.description: North Idaho luxury living at its finest! This amazing custom home on nearly 5 acres is nestled amongst evergreens with breathtaking views of Schweitzer Mountain and Cape Horn Peak. Live in rural splendor within minutes of Athol Crossings, Bayview, boat launches, Farragut State Park, and thousands of acres of recreation land! This custom-built home has abundant amenities, including a stunning primary suite, gourmet kitchen, 3 fireplaces, a theater/media room, and a full kitchen in the daylight walkout basement! The wrap-around decks, ideal for entertaining, include an outdoor see-through fireplace and a private deck off the master bedroom. The upstairs bonus room of over 750 square feet comes with a full bath and custom built-ins! The fully-finished, attached, 3-car garage is heated and includes a drive-thru bay. The driveway is newly paved and includes circular turn-around and ample amount of space for parking. Owner/Agent
